searchData={"items":[{"type":"module","title":"AutoGrader","doc":"An automatic and concurrent assignments grading program.","ref":"AutoGrader.html"},{"type":"module","title":"Lifecycle - AutoGrader","doc":"1. INIT - `AutoGrader`:\n  - runs the potential init `AutoGrader.SetupUnit`\n  - list submissions from specified directory\n  - starts one supervised `AutoGrader.SubmissionRunner` per submission\n\n2. PROCESSING - `AutoGrader.SubmissionRunner` (for each submission)\n  - runs the `AutoGrader.SetupUnit`s sequentially (in supervised tasks)\n  - runs all `AutoGrader.TestUnit`s concurrently (in supervised tasks)\n  - handles `AutoGrader.TestUnit`s completion messages as they arrive\n  - waits for all processes to complete, crash or time out\n  - calculates the submission's score\n  - sends back the final score and detailed results to `AutoGrader`\n\n3. COMPLETING - `AutoGrader`\n  - waits for all `AutoGrader.SubmissionRunner` processes to complete\n  - displays final score and detailed results for all submissions","ref":"AutoGrader.html#module-lifecycle"},{"type":"function","title":"AutoGrader.child_spec/1","doc":"Returns a specification to start this module under a supervisor.\n\nSee `Supervisor`.","ref":"AutoGrader.html#child_spec/1"},{"type":"function","title":"AutoGrader.start_link/2","doc":"","ref":"AutoGrader.html#start_link/2"},{"type":"module","title":"AutoGrader.Application","doc":"","ref":"AutoGrader.Application.html"},{"type":"behaviour","title":"AutoGrader.SetupUnit","doc":"A behavior for defining setup units.","ref":"AutoGrader.SetupUnit.html"},{"type":"behaviour","title":"Submission setup unit - AutoGrader.SetupUnit","doc":"Setup units run sequentially in each submissions before running test units.\n\nAs their name suggest, they are used to run setup actions before running the\ntest suites, like installing dependencies.\n\nThey receive and return a `context` map, which will be passed to every test\nunit, so they can also be used to load/generate data that a lot of tests are\ngoing to use, like parsing the Git log history.\n\nBecause setup units run sequentially, they receive the `context` map returned\nby the previous setup unit.\n\nIf a setup unit fails, the whole submission will fail.","ref":"AutoGrader.SetupUnit.html#module-submission-setup-unit"},{"type":"behaviour","title":"Init setup unit - AutoGrader.SetupUnit","doc":"An `init_setup_unit` can also be provided in the config. This setup unit will\nbe run only once on startup, before starting to process submissions.\n\nThe `context` map it returns is then passed down to the first regular setup\nunit, or directly to the test units if no regular setup units are defined.","ref":"AutoGrader.SetupUnit.html#module-init-setup-unit"},{"type":"callback","title":"AutoGrader.SetupUnit.run/2","doc":"Runs the setup unit","ref":"AutoGrader.SetupUnit.html#c:run/2"},{"type":"callback","title":"AutoGrader.SetupUnit.timeout/0","doc":"The timeout (ms) after which to kill the setup unit if it hasn't completed","ref":"AutoGrader.SetupUnit.html#c:timeout/0"},{"type":"module","title":"AutoGrader.SubmissionRunner","doc":"","ref":"AutoGrader.SubmissionRunner.html"},{"type":"function","title":"AutoGrader.SubmissionRunner.child_spec/1","doc":"Returns a specification to start this module under a supervisor.\n\nSee `Supervisor`.","ref":"AutoGrader.SubmissionRunner.html#child_spec/1"},{"type":"function","title":"AutoGrader.SubmissionRunner.start_link/2","doc":"","ref":"AutoGrader.SubmissionRunner.html#start_link/2"},{"type":"behaviour","title":"AutoGrader.TestUnit","doc":"A behavior for defining test units.\n\nThe `run/2` callback is called to run the test unit, and must return a\n`{score, max_score}` tuple.\n\nThe potential context generated from setup units will be passed as a second\nargument.\n\nA `coefficient/0` callback *can* be defined to modify the coefficient of the\ntest unit (defaults to `1`).\n\nA `bonus?/0` callback *can* be defined to treat the test unit as a bonus\nexercice (defaults to `false`).","ref":"AutoGrader.TestUnit.html"},{"type":"function","title":"AutoGrader.TestUnit.bonus?/0","doc":"","ref":"AutoGrader.TestUnit.html#bonus?/0"},{"type":"callback","title":"AutoGrader.TestUnit.bonus?/0","doc":"Whether or not this test unit is a bonus one.","ref":"AutoGrader.TestUnit.html#c:bonus?/0"},{"type":"function","title":"AutoGrader.TestUnit.coefficient/0","doc":"","ref":"AutoGrader.TestUnit.html#coefficient/0"},{"type":"callback","title":"AutoGrader.TestUnit.coefficient/0","doc":"The coefficient to apply to this test unit.","ref":"AutoGrader.TestUnit.html#c:coefficient/0"},{"type":"callback","title":"AutoGrader.TestUnit.run/2","doc":"Runs the test unit.\n\nReturns a `{score, max_score}` tuple.","ref":"AutoGrader.TestUnit.html#c:run/2"}],"content_type":"text/markdown","producer":{"name":"ex_doc","version":[48,46,51,52,46,48]}}